data.description: Move in Ready! This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home is ready for it's new owner! The home features an open floor plan with the living room, dining room and kitchen all situated on the first floor with sliding glass doors leading out the the large deck. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and tile backslash. Upstairs you will find a large master suite with a separate sitting room and 3 closets one with a built-in safe. This home also features a two door/two car garage and a large Corner Lot!! Just minutes from area shopping, restaurants and Fort Liberty. It is time for you to STOP looking you have found the place to call HOME!
